post_title: Ups and Downs Caravan Park Farm Stay

post_content: A small clearing by the path, room for about one to two small tents.
Redbank Hut bush camping area is an open cleared area near the old Redbank Hut.

Nebine Creek camping area is an open area shaded by coolibah trees. The camping area can be reached by 4WD (only). It is accessible for high clearance off-road camper trailers only. It is not accessible for caravans and buses.
